                    bibendum, dui pede condimentum odio, ac blandit ante orci ut diam. <a href="index.html">
                        Read more...</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1>
                    Chi ha realizzato BusBook?</h1>
                <p class="SliderFontstyle">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Donec libero. Suspendisse
                    bibendum. Cras id urna. Morbi tincidunt, orci ac convallis aliquam, lectus turpis
                    varius lorem, eu posuere nunc justo tempus leo. Donec mattis, purus nec placerat
                    bibendum, dui pede condimentum odio, ac blandit ante orci ut diam. <a href="index.html">
                        Read more...</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="../../Content/scripts/slides.min.jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
        <script>
            $(function () {
                $('#slides').slides({
                    play: 5000,
                    pause: 5000,
                    hoverPause: true
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</div>
<!--end content-->
<div id="sidebar">
    <div id="hire">
        <h2 class="sidebar-title">
            Login</h2>
        <p>
            @{
                Html.RenderAction("ShowLogin", "Login", Session.getLoggedUtente());
            }
        </p>
    </div>
    <!--end hire-->
